        <h3>What is euromancer@emag?</h3>
        <p>euromancer@emag is an open-source self-publishing platform inspired by Eastern Bloc samizdat practices, modern command-line interfaces, and early diskmag subculture. 
        <br>The platform is currently in active development ‚ÄĒ its source code is publicly <a href="https://github.com/aleglutz/cli-izdat" target="_blank">available on GitHub</a>. 
        <br>Visual and text references are collected in the <a href="https://www.are.na/aleg-lutz/cli-izdat" target="_blank">CLI-izdat channel</a> on Are.na.</p>
